OL,3,CRace Equality Hub opens in Liverpool
OL,5,FRacial inequality in is being tackled
OL,6,Fhead on with more than #2 million
OL,7,Finvested in a Race Equality Hub.
OL,9,FThe aim of the hub is to support
OL,10,Femployers and agencies to enable
OL,11,FBlack, Asian and Minority Ethnic
OL,12,Fbusinesses to thrive.
OL,14,Fhas opened the Hub at a special event
