OL,3,CRace Equality Hub opens in Liverpool
OL,5,FBig name employers like Lloyds Bank,
OL,6,FHays Recruitment and the Department
OL,7,Ffor Work and Pensions have signed up
OL,8,Fto work with the project.
OL,10,FAlison Navarro, Programme Director of
OL,11,Fthe Race Equality Hub said:
OL,13,F"So often people from Black, Asian and
OL,14,FMinority Ethnic communities aren't
OL,15,Fshort of the qualifications or desire,
OL,16,Fbut are short of the opportunities.
