OL,3,CRace Equality Hub opens in Liverpool
OL,5,F"Working together with our communities
OL,6,FI am confident that the Race Equality
OL,7,FHub will radically improve
OL,8,Fopportunities for all of our
OL,9,Fcommunities' members."
OL,11,FSteve Rotheram, Mayor of the Liverpool
OL,12,FCity Region, said:
OL,14,F"It is truly unique because no area
OL,15,Fhas done this before - and I am
OL,16,Fexcited to watch Alison and her team
OL,17,Fdrive our vision forward."
