OL,3,CRace Equality Hub opens in Liverpool
OL,5,FThe launch comes after the recent
OL,6,Fannouncement of a new advisory board
OL,7,Fof 14 people from Black, Asian and
OL,8,FMinority Ethnic backgrounds across the
OL,9,FLiverpool City who will oversee the
OL,10,Fwork of the ground-breaking Hub.
OL,12,FMayor Rotheram's racial equality
OL,13,Fprogramme forms part of his strategy
OL,14,Fto ensure no communities are left
OL,15,Fbehind and aims to tackle racial
OL,16,Finequality across the Liverpool City
OL,17,FRegion.
